-         kdel(isp, jsp) = 2.0_wp/((1.0_wp / ps_h0_diat_scale(3, izp)) &
-            & + (1.0_wp / ps_h0_diat_scale(3, jzp)))
+         ! Harmonic mean, written in a zero-safe form. A zero parameter marks
+         ! an angular-momentum channel which is absent for that element (for
+         ! example the p channel of hydrogen), and its pair scaling therefore
+         ! has the well-defined limiting value zero.
